&lt;li&gt;Prepare quarterly financial statements and capital account statements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain and update fund accounting data across systems, including data cleanup projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track task completion against service-level agreements (SLAs) and escalate issues when needed&lt;/li&gt;
